                  "width": 2,
                  "height": 0
                },
                "weight_g": 0
              }
            ],
            "usage_notes": "Pogo pin pads should be 1.5-2mm diameter minimum for reliable contact. Gold plating recommended for better contact. Place on bottom PCB with no solder mask over pads.",
            "compatibility_notes": "Compatible with standard spring-loaded pogo pins (1A-3A current rating typical). Ensure mating pogo pins have sufficient spring force (typically 20-50g per pin).",
            "warnings": [
              "Do not cover pads with solder mask - must remain exposed copper",
              "Ensure bottom PCB surface remains flat - no components on this side",
              "Pogo pin diameter typically 0.8-1.5mm - design pads accordingly"
            ],
