              "manufacturer": "Microchip Technology",
              "part_number": "ATTINY85-20SU",
              "description": "Microchip ATtiny85 8-bit AVR RISC microcontroller in 8-lead SOIC narrow body (8S2) SMT package. Same die as the PDIP-8 ATTINY85-20PU: 8 KB flash, 512 B SRAM, 512 B EEPROM, 6 GPIO (PB0-PB5; PB5 = RESET by default), 3 hardware PWM (OC0A/PB0, OC0B/PB1, OC1B/PB4), 4-channel 10-bit ADC, USI bit-banged 3-wire SPI + I2C, pin-change interrupts on every I/O, internal 8 MHz RC (16 MHz via PLL), 2.7-5.5 V, -40..85 degC industrial. SOIC-8 is the reflow-assembled production form factor.",
              "datasheet_url": "https://ww1.microchip.com/downloads/en/DeviceDoc/Atmel-2586-AVR-8-bit-Microcontroller-ATtiny25-ATtiny45-ATtiny85_Datasheet.pdf",
