              "Do not bend tighter than 30° at any single point.",
              "PWM dimming above 200 Hz to avoid visible flicker.",
              "Cut from 300mm stock: 12 LED dies (~18mm active) + 3mm stripped silicone per end = 24mm total. Leaves ~1mm margin per side in 20mm PCB slot.",
