              "datasheet_url": "",
              "purchase_url": "https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DGPY5WLZ",
              "description": "LISOCLU flexible cool-white (6500K) LED filament cut to 24mm from 300mm stock. 12 micro LED dies in parallel on FPC substrate, silicone-coated. 18mm active LED area fits in 20mm PCB slot with 1mm margin per side. 3mm stripped silicone per end for soldering. Double-ended: anode on one end, cathode opposite. ~3V Vf, 50mA max continuous (25mm Adafruit reference). PWM dimmable. CRI 85. Amazon ASIN B0DGPY5WLZ.",
              "id": "basic-sv2zTkkdEoWhSKry9Vqp9",
