            },
            "usage_notes": "Flexible cool-white LED filament cut from 300mm stock to 24mm total (18mm active LEDs + 3mm stripped per end). Sits in 20mm PCB slot with ~1mm clearance per side. Two-terminal polarized LED load needing external resistor. Double-ended: V+ and GND on opposite ends, stripped and soldered to PCB pads.",
            "application_examples": [
              "Maker Chip PCB recessed LED accent lighting",
              "Three-channel individually PWM-dimmable cool-white indicators",
              "Pattern-programmable LED effects via ATtiny85",
              "Custom-length accent lighting (cut to fit PCB slot)"
            ]
