        {
          "id": "761a92ab-953c-4ffd-ae31-4092684c9e06",
          "title": "Order components (Amazon + LCSC/DigiKey)",
          "description": "Order 1+ pack LISOCLU HUAN159 300mm cool-white 6500K double-ended flexible LED filaments (Amazon ASIN B0DGPY5WLZ, ~$1.99/2pcs — will cut to 24mm, yields ~12 filaments per 300mm stock piece, need 3 minimum). Order 3+ YAGEO RC0603FR-0756RL 56 Ω 1% 0603 resistors (DigiKey 311-56.0HRCT-ND, ~$0.10 ea), and 1+ ATtiny85-20SU SOIC-8 (LCSC C89852). Order extras for spares. Changed from Adafruit ADA-6141 warm white to LISOCLU cool white for double-ended connection and Amazon return policy.",
