        {
          "id": "ba71565a-c523-46c0-9321-910f1b654f46",
          "title": "Publish 4 ProtoPart library PRs",
          "description": "Four local branches in worktrees ready (none pushed): new/attiny85 (6c18918, PDIP-8), new/attiny85-soic8 (ea70485, SOIC-8), new/adafruit-ada-6141-warm-white-filament (dd23f20), new/yageo-rc0603-56r-1pct (6f5f92a). Awaiting user go-ahead to push branches and open PRs. Decide before publish whether to roll the resistor count:1 tweak into the library def or leave canonical count:2 (board has the tweak applied, library def doesn't).",
