          "id": "f1481c33-b11e-401b-a181-54ae58a69a36",
          "title": "Decide on ATtiny↔Filament schema mismatch",
          "description": "3 ATtiny↔Filament harnesses are INCOMPATIBLE in DRC because canonical PWM is `digital,output` and filament input is `power,input`. Electrically valid (36 mA/pin within AVR limits). Options: (a) accept the schema-only red, (b) add 3 N-MOSFETs and rewire (extra parts, schema goes green), (c) keep the board's ATtiny template specialized with `power,output` interfaces for PWM pins (board-local fudge, canonical lives only in library). Currently option (a) is in effect.",
          "status": "todo",
