          "title": "Roll resistor count:1 tweak into library def",
          "description": "Protoboard board template uses `requires.power_bus.count:1 shareable_with` so a single interface can serve two harnesses (one per terminal). The canonical agent-produced def on `new/yageo-rc0603-56r-1pct` keeps `count:2`. Decide before publishing whether to roll the tweak into the library version (cleaner per-harness allocation) or leave the canonical shape and tweak only on board templates.",
          "status": "todo",
          "createdAt": 1778795173086,
          "updatedAt": 1778795173086
        },
