          "title": "Unlinked Harness: ATtiny85 → Warm Filament 2 (Incompatible)",
          "content": "**Issue:** Harness has no interface link configured.\\n\\n**Status:** INCOMPATIBLE - No compatible interface pairs found.\\n\\n**Analysis:** Same as Warm Filament 1. ATtiny85 PWM output (5V logic level) cannot directly drive LED filament power interface.\\n\\n**Required Action:** Link LED filament through the 56Ω resistor (part: 235f61f0-9250-479f-8607-1556cc1e5817) to route PWM from MCU to LED.\\n\\n**Current Circuit State:**\\n- Resistor 2 is already connected: Filament 2 → Resistor 2 → GND\\n- Missing: MCU PWM → Resistor 2\\n\\nSee Warm Filament 1 comment for full remediation.\",\n<parameter name=\"entityId\">77e1affc-3363-46ae-9285-2a47068928f3\",\n<parameter name=\"entityType\">harness",
